Privacy Policy

App Name: Timerify

Last updated: 12.10.2024

1. Introduction
Timerfily is a simple timer application designed to help users manage their daily activities efficiently. The app is entirely user-focused, and we place great importance on user privacy.

2. Data Collection
This app does not collect any personal information. We do not collect, store, or use any personal data such as name, email address, location, or any other personal information. The app operates entirely locally on the user's device and does not require an internet connection to function.

3. Use of Data
Since Timerify does not collect any data, there is no data processing, sharing, or storage involved. All the features of the app work locally on the user's device, and no information is shared with third parties.

4. Commitment to User Privacy
At Timerify, we highly value the privacy of our users. We do not collect any data now, and there will be no data collection or processes that compromise user privacy in the future.

5. Third-Party Services
This app does not integrate with any third-party services. Therefore, no data is transferred to any external services or providers.

6. Contact
If you have any questions about our privacy policy, please feel free to contact us:

Email: moonapp@outlook.com.tr
